title: Anyone unable to select ranked queue?
body:
You can pick all game modes, but not sub game modes, ie you can pick summoners rift, but you cannot select flex, solo/duo queue etc.

Is this happening for anyone else?

replies.body: Ranked is currently down in the lead-up to maintenance that begins at 1AM AEST this morning. Check out [this thread](https://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/announcements/kor6fXjT-oce-platform-maintenance-2017-05-10-100am-aest) for more details on the maintenance!
mine is working fine, RIOT made a thread of this few days before, if you are having such issue means your client get corrupt you need to re-install the client mate :) hope it helps
